&lt;p&gt;마지막으로 들린 곳.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;원래는 이후에 한군데를 더 들리려 했는데, 주차장으로 들어가려는 차가 너무 많이 기다리고 있어서 그냥 집에가자 하셨음. 나중에 평일에 한번 다시 모시고 가야지.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="320px" data-flex-grow="133" height="6048" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/19.jpg" srcset="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/19_hu_18a6eca6d555ec13.jpg 800w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/19_hu_c747f40c2ffcbae9.jpg 1600w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/19_hu_cc61f5e071ba433a.jpg 2400w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/19.jpg 8064w" width="8064"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;들어가자 마자 보인 프리지아. 그래서 마로니에 칵테일 사랑이 생각났다. 그런 의미에서 경서 버전으로&amp;hellip;?!?!?!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="180px" data-flex-grow="75" height="8064" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/20.jpg" srcset="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/20_hu_21ad16795e095a42.jpg 800w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/20_hu_642ce960da85f3da.jpg 1600w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/20_hu_a3dfa82d2d4bb8b6.jpg 2400w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/20.jpg 6048w" width="6048"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;검은색 꽃이 신기하고 이뻐서 찍었는데, 막 찍었더니 초점이 안맞네&amp;hellip;.좀 더 신경써서 찍을걸..ㅠ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="180px" data-flex-grow="75" height="4032" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/21.jpg" srcset="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/21_hu_1cb615aad95e82d.jpg 800w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/21_hu_74dadbdeb6157c1b.jpg 1600w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/21_hu_82755eff85b87375.jpg 2400w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/21.jpg 3024w" width="3024"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="180px" data-flex-grow="75" height="8064" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/22.jpg" srcset="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/22_hu_7d3d7b45bceea0ab.jpg 800w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/22_hu_5bc334ae45f60032.jpg 1600w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/22_hu_4cf079d0fbe2280c.jpg 2400w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/22.jpg 6048w" width="6048"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;완전 펴져서, 평면으로 보였다. 접시같이 생기고 이쁜 꽃!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="180px" data-flex-grow="75" height="4032" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/23.jpg" srcset="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/23_hu_607ecaa7ae58eefe.jpg 800w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/23_hu_ed3f7b7be7876a52.jpg 1600w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/23_hu_257b14182812f703.jpg 2400w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/23.jpg 3024w" width="3024"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이건 엄마가 찍어놓으래서 찍어놨는데, 엄마도 나도 까먹&amp;hellip;.구매하시려고 하셨던 거 같은데.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="180px" data-flex-grow="75" height="8064" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/24.jpg" srcset="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/24_hu_fe687545243d98e4.jpg 800w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/24_hu_c76b7ebb875f7a9b.jpg 1600w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/24_hu_ad8567429f604ea7.jpg 2400w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/24.jpg 6048w" width="6048"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;빨강 노랑 꽃들을 섞어서 배치해놔서, 사진보다 더 이뻤다. 확실히 눈보다 더 좋은 인풋 하드웨어가 없는거 같다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="180px" data-flex-grow="75" height="8064" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/25.jpg" srcset="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/25_hu_343441bbaedd690.jpg 800w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/25_hu_d46c360d7e43667a.jpg 1600w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/25_hu_b1a02c4c45ef7b53.jpg 2400w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/25.jpg 6048w" width="6048"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;남자는 핑크지! 사실 분홍과 보라색 사이 어딘가의 색이었음&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="180px" data-flex-grow="75" height="8064" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/26.jpg" srcset="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/26_hu_9ed5353a951f5328.jpg 800w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/26_hu_ba9d90aa04769206.jpg 1600w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/26_hu_ba2ceac1c2b7e264.jpg 2400w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/26.jpg 6048w" width="6048"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;둘 중 무엇을 살 까 고민하시던 어무이는&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="180px" data-flex-grow="75" height="8064" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/27.jpg" srcset="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/27_hu_74c821927cce0f04.jpg 800w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/27_hu_a41083e17a3ecbe.jpg 1600w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/27_hu_9196bb777b656863.jpg 2400w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/27.jpg 6048w" width="6048"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;짜잔! 둘 다 선택&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="180px" data-flex-grow="75" height="8064" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/28.jpg" srcset="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/28_hu_a773725663e8d28a.jpg 800w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/28_hu_a6c004e6810a27aa.jpg 1600w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/28_hu_c1db28f1e6b40bb3.jpg 2400w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/28.jpg 6048w" width="6048"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이건 아까 위에 평면과는 완전 반대로, 반원형으로 엄청 입체적으로 피고 있어서 신기했다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="180px" data-flex-grow="75" height="8064" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/29.jpg" srcset="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/29_hu_12a0505fe3a330c4.jpg 800w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/29_hu_7db92bb8d36eb38a.jpg 1600w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/29_hu_acc0cd94dc6a019b.jpg 2400w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/29.jpg 6048w" width="6048"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;파란색 vs 분홍색&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="180px" data-flex-grow="75" height="4032" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/30.jpg" srcset="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/30_hu_646f6a4224fbc4ea.jpg 800w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/30_hu_f47733a4bba7f169.jpg 1600w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/30_hu_616ce24d736c9fd3.jpg 2400w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/30.jpg 3024w" width="3024"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이것도 종이공예 같았다. 엄청 오묘하고 이쁜 색. 그라데이션 느낌도 나는.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="180px" data-flex-grow="75" height="8064" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/31.jpg" srcset="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/31_hu_7876cc1b61fd49b9.jpg 800w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/31_hu_2efb458bf16cc7be.jpg 1600w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/31_hu_3cf97e7e2001b1c6.jpg 2400w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/31.jpg 6048w" width="6048"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="180px" data-flex-grow="75" height="8064" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/32.jpg" srcset="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/32_hu_4e00c57680dc25cb.jpg 800w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/32_hu_e437f7c41cbdb1d2.jpg 1600w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/32_hu_2dc7d43543ee6f5c.jpg 2400w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/32.jpg 6048w" width="6048"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;회색에 가까운 초록색. 많이 어두운 느낌의 이파리를 가지고 있는데, 꽃은 정말 화사한 노랑이라 뭔가&amp;hellip;절망 가운데서 핀 희망 같은 느낌? 이었다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="180px" data-flex-grow="75" height="8064" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/33.jpg" srcset="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/33_hu_82e247c2c4a8120b.jpg 800w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/33_hu_13c7ce77171f64db.jpg 1600w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/33_hu_1d614950ba48bda.jpg 2400w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040504/33.jpg 6048w" width="6048"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;그렇게 구경하는 사이에 하나 더!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;저녁 뭐먹을까 고민하다가, 일요일 1 + 1 도미노피자로 픽! 운전하느라 내가 시킬 수가 없어서 동생한테 시키라고 했더니 엄마가 자조섞인 말을 아버지한테 건네셨다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;ldquo;우리는 도움이 안되는 사람들이야. 피자도 못시키고..&amp;rdquo;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;예전에, 키오스크 하실 줄 몰라서 햄버거 못사드셨다고 했던 게 문득 생각나서 슬펐다. 이번에 쉬는 기간동안 부모님 모시고 여기저기 많이 다녀야겠다..&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PS&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/C8L14GcvFPw?si=hpBnrth3GjlBKB-8" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;p&gt;날씨가 좋아서 그런건지, 식목일이라 그런건지, 주말이라 그런건지, 커플들이 엄청 많더라. 신혼부부로 보이는 사람들도 많고&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;봄이 좋냐! 멍청이들아!!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>남사 화훼단지 리뷰 - 2</title><link>https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040503/</link><pubDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2026 17:08:31 +0900</pubDate><guid>https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040503/</guid><description>&lt;iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/OxgiiyLp5pk?si=AzoVuBtJaLvN2Tzp" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
